Ingestion
---------
->Chunking:fixed size chunking; semantic chunking(LangChain, LlamaIndex); document aware chunking(used for pdfs); Hierarchical chunking(structured documents, its used)

Embedding models
----------------
->Numerical vector that represents the meaning of the text
->Whn user asks a question, the system also converts the query into embedding and searches for the relevant match. Its called semantic search
->Text-embedding-3-large from openAI
->voyage-3 from voyage AI 
->open-source models like bge-large and E5-mistral available on Hugging Face

